Introducing Yokee with Video:
- Record a video as you perform your song.
- Select from a variety of video themes (Snow, Old, Love, Cute and many more).
- Spice your video with real time video animation FX.
- Add a personal intro to your video.

Holidays are almost here and we have tons of new stuff for you:
- Create a musical greeting cards and send to your acquaintances.
- Holidays songs & Christmas carols playlist is ready for you to sing.
- New "Holidays" and "Rain" themes are now available for your video recordings. Check them out, both are super cool!
- Your recordings are now synced with your profile so you can access them anywhere and never lose them.
- We've dressed the app icon for the holidays. Hope you'll like it
- The app is fully compatible with the latest and greatest of Apple's iOS9.

We are always here at your service, shoot us an email to support@yokee.tv if you have any problems.

Hey singers,

We have a huge update for you with dozens of new features and improvments.

- New tab bar navigation to make it easier to access the app sections.
- New Performances feed tab with the hottest covers created by users in the Yokee Community.
- We've redesigned our lyrics player and added support to both portrait and landscape.
- New user account section to make sure your recording are always safe.
- You can now change the name and album art of your video recording before saving or sharing it.
- New 'Fire' video theme

Hey folks!
We got a huge update for you:
- Songbook redesign which include songs previews and artwork.
- On-boarding flow to help you choose the right songs to sing.
- 'Recommended' playlist with songs which match your singing history.
- Cool new Video FXs (GLING, 80s, SCI-FI and Animation).
- Back camera support for video.
- Realtime indications when your lighting is too bright or dart during video.
- Realtime indication when your mic volume is too low.

Please keep sending us feedback at support@yokee.tv

Hey Yokees!
We got a huge update for you:
- Brand new singing player
* a professional audio FXs bar which allow to tune the FX parameters.
* Ability to mark successful points in the songs and go back to them later.
* Easy camera on/off switch
* Great sharing save and sharing experience
- A cappella style songs
- Support iPad Portrait
- Allow to add album art and description to video and non-video recordings
- iOS 10 compatibility
- Get notified when your recording is ready!
- Many more fixes and enhancements.

Happy Singing!

• Search by Songs, Users and Tags and view your recent searches.
• Like, Comment and Follow other singers.
• Customize your public profile and choose which performances to share.
